title: (Tues Early Bird) STOLEN Item from the Studio…Bobby Gives Someone on the Show A Chance To Come Clean + Bobby Feud: First Thing We Do in the Morning
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) STOLEN Item from the Studio…Bobby Gives Someone on the Show A Chance To Come Clean + Bobby Feud: First Thing We Do in the Morning
description:
Bobby addresses a recent controversy he had with a country artist after something was stolen from the studio. He gives everyone a chance to come clean before enforcing a MAJOR punishment. Inside of the Bobby Feud, the show tries to name the Top 10 things Americans do in the morning.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
